An Interview with Matthew Ball About the Vision Pro and the State of Gaming
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

This interview is lightly edited for clarity.

*Topics:*
Metaverse Terminology ( #metaverse ) | Apple Vision Pro ( #avp ) | Apple TV=
+ ( #appletv ) | The State of Gaming ( #gaming ) | Generative AI and Gaming=
